To find reference to the views in a fragment, use the parent view. `getView()` returns the parent view after `onCreateView()` and since you are calling `updateNavHeader()` inside the `onCreateView()` its getting null.

So, either you can initialize all your view in the `onCreate()` itself or make the `view` global so that you can access it anywhere.

```
 @Override
    public View onCreateView(LayoutInflater inflater, ViewGroup container,
                             Bundle savedInstanceState) {
       
